data.description: One of the most desirable neighborhoods in Palm Beach Gardens with pickleball, pool and tennis and low HOA.  This 2 bedroom, 2 bath villa has a magnificent new pool with jaw dropping lighting, new sand blasted Calcatta deck and easy to maintain turf. New flooring in both bathrooms, laundry room, kitchen  and living room. Renovated walk in shower, custom made pantry, plus outside and inside painted.  Both bedrooms have an en suite.  The pool lights  at night are stunning! Switch to blue or green and you will feel like your in a tropical resort.   This is a must see!  TURN KEY!
